<paragraph blockId="22.[178,1085,512,592]" pageId="22" pageNumber="951">
D i s t r i b u t i o n: from central and south-eastern 
<collectingCountry box="[742,811,512,533]" name="France" pageId="22" pageNumber="951">France</collectingCountry>
through central Europe to 
<collectingCountry box="[178,265,541,563]" name="Bulgaria" pageId="22" pageNumber="951">Bulgaria</collectingCountry>
and northern 
<collectingCountry box="[411,485,541,563]" name="Greece" pageId="22" pageNumber="951">Greece</collectingCountry>
, southern 
<collectingCountry box="[592,673,541,563]" name="Ukraine" pageId="22" pageNumber="951">Ukraine</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion box="[688,768,541,563]" country="Ukraine" name="Crimea" pageId="22" pageNumber="951">Crimea</collectingRegion>
), Transcaucasia, north-western and southern 
<collectingCountry box="[314,390,570,592]" name="Turkey" pageId="22" pageNumber="951">Turkey</collectingCountry>
, north-western 
<collectingCountry box="[547,604,570,592]" name="Syria" pageId="22" pageNumber="951">Syria</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="22.[178,1085,608,659]" pageId="22" pageNumber="951">
